Line1.541E6: And what a great ugly thing it is... Glorious.
Line10.541E6: And congratulations, warrior of the Oxen Tribe.
Line8.541E6: I will deliver this to the Forgemaster. When you are ready, return to us in Ked Bardu.
VoiceDir1.541E6: Admiring the gnarled beast's severed head. Smiling. Wolfish.
